Class ProcessListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • ecoware.ecowareprocessor.ProcessListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ECoWareMessageListener

    public class ProcessListener
extends Object
implements ECoWareMessageListener
    Author:
    Armando Varriale

    This class is an implementation of the ECoWareMessageListener interface. In particular, its "notify" method simply forward the message notified to the Eper Provider for the subsequent processing phases.
